hat there are too many foreign coaches in the Super Eagles’ technical team. April 10, 2019 In "Sports" Ex-Nigeria international Sam Sodje has said that the announcement of French coach Paul Le Guen as Super Eagles coach without reaching an agreement with him was unprofessional and an embarrassment to the nation. July 21, 2016 In "Sports" NFF The Nigeria Football Federation, NFF, says it has asked Super Eagles’ Technical Adviser, Mr. Gernot Rohr to explain reasons behind several breaches of the contract that he signed with the body, which forbids him to divulge to the public/media information on some aspects of the contract. Speaking in Abuja… November 27, 2019 In "News"